Elegant 2800 sq/ft All Brick home in Royal Glen Subdivision! 4 Bd, 2.5 Ba; You’ll love this Floor plan; Formal Dining, Den w/Fireplace, Hardwoods, Ceramic Tile. Luxurious Master Suite downstairs; Luxury Master Bath to include double vanities, whirlpool tub, separate shower, and large walk-in closet. Large Bonus Room over garage, professionally landscaped with goldfish pond, large lot, and much more! Conveniently located! Blackman Schools! 

Home Trades Welcome!! Financing Available! 

To view home anytime, call 877-633-3688 ext. 2 or visit www.quicklysellyourhome.com.
